                    <h1 style="color: #1DA31A; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 34px; font-weight: 400;">Technical Issues with the Website</h1>
                    
                    <p>"I'm experiencing technical issues while using the website, such as slow loading times or error messages. How can I troubleshoot these issues?"</p>

                    <section style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                        <ul>
                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Check Internet Connection
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>Ensure that your internet connection is stable. Slow loading times may result from a poor or unstable connection. Try refreshing the page or restarting your internet router.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Browser Compatibility
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>Confirm that you are using a supported browser. Outdated browsers may not be optimized for the website's features, leading to performance issues</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Clear Browser Cache and Cookies
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>Over time, accumulated cache and cookies can impact website performance. Clear your browser's cache and cookies to ensure a fresh start. Instructions for doing this vary based on the browser you are using.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Disable Browser Extensions
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>Some browser extensions may interfere with website functionality. Temporarily disable browser extensions or try using an incognito/private browsing window to see if the issue persists</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> Update Browser
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>Ensure that your browser or mobile app is up-to-date. Developers often release updates to improve performance, security, and compatibility.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> Try Another Device
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>If possible, try accessing the website/app from a different device. This helps determine whether the issue is specific to your device or more widespread.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> Contact Technical Support
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>If the problem persists after trying the above steps, reach out to our technical support team for assistance.</li>
                                     <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                         <li>Email: Contact us at <a href="mailto:greensupermartlk@gmail.com" style="color: #1DA31A;">greensupermartlk@gmail.com</a> with specific details about the issue, including error messages, and any troubleshooting steps you've already taken.</li>
                                         <li>Messaging Box: You can also send us a message directly from the message box in the <a href="../helpCenter.jsp" style="color: #1DA31A;">Help Center</a>.</li>
                                     </ol>
                                </ol>
                            </li>

                            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> Report Error Messages
                                <ol style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 20px;">
                                     <li>If you encounter error messages, take note of them and include the details when contacting technical support. This information assists the support team in diagnosing and resolving the issue more efficiently.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </section>
                    
                    
                        
                        
